author: Devan McGuinness
title: Maisie Williams looked straight up like the dancer emoji at the Brit Awards last night
text:
Maisie Williams looked straight up like the dancer emoji at the Brit Awards last night It was a big night for our favorite British stars as they all gathered to celebrate the Brit Awards last night. One of our fave leading ladies, Maisie Williams, was in attendance at the 2017 Brit Awards and her dress was pure perfection. Williams chose an outfit that made her look like the dancer emoji’s identical twin. 
The 19-year-old “Game of Thrones” star arrived wearing a gorgeous red gown that looked super comfortable. We’re all for fashion that doesn’t make us count down the seconds until we can get home and breathe again.
But, her gown had her looking like a close resemblance to one of our favorite emoji’s too — the dancer! The star posted a photo to Instagram, and her pose was total #twinning. A post shared by Maisie Williams (@maisie_williams) on Feb 23, 2017 at 3:22am PST 
Holding up the bottom of her dress with one hand, while her other arm was up in the air was the perfect mimic to the loved emoji. That, paired with her chin-length brown hair, and her adorable smile, she was an exact double.
She captioned the photo, “Lemme do the thing like the emoji” .”
David M. Benett/Dave Benett/ Getty Images for Warner Music Earlier on her Instagram feed, she posted a photo of herself and British musical artist Stormz, fangirling out while she smiled.
A post shared by Maisie Williams (@maisie_williams) on Feb 23, 2017 at 3:10am PST 
“But then this happened and I lost my shit,” she wrote with the photo.
She’s seriously always such a ray of sunshine!
